Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.53,0:00:05.23,bitoshi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(439,372)}-2年前 西伯利亞-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 流星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 在哪 在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在流星墜地之前把願望說三遍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.13,0:00:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個願望就會實現 是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.68,0:00:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是日本的民間巫咒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前從你媽媽那裡聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他還有變成美女的巫咒或長個子的巫咒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.99,0:00:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在許什麼願
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.01,0:00:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現流星就意味著有人死去 這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:01:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少能看到真正的星空的時候 這只是個傳說而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.07,0:01:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.72,0:01:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.67,0:01:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘇芳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是兩年前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.01,0:02:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個被稱為「東京大爆炸」事件發生的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑成為了契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:18.31,bitoshi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(439,372)}-2年後 符拉迪沃斯托克-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就香煙的煙來說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二手煙比一手煙的有害物質更多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高致癌性的二甲基亞硝胺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一手煙的含量為5.3-43微克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而二手煙的含量則為680-823微克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奎林含量在二手煙裡的含量則是一手煙的11倍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大約還有18000微克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使這樣 要俄羅斯人不吸煙也是絕對不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘管大家都知道 理性的思考來說最好還是戒掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是除非變成傳說中的契約者 不然就無法做到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 有聽過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些星星隕落是因為有契約者死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的存在嗎 那樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的話想見識下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別拿我開玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是危險分子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩的事情已經夠多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一杯1968年的格倫荻佛龍 純的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窖藏了33年的雪利酒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說在這家店的滯銷品裡發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人 您怎麼會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是April吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是August7
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被稱為魔術師的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經向俄羅斯當局透露了情報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,FSB兩天後會進行搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}FSB 俄羅斯聯邦保安局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了收集好的數據外都放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,July呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你經常和蘇芳在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都在關注你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都很在意你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那不是尼卡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能腦袋不聰明而且老是打架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我一定會好好珍惜你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想好好珍惜你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請和我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是告白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行嗎 和我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎 真的行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:05:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可以一起回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等會兒見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘇芳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是肯定的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是偶然 偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 那個照相機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為塔尼亞當時的表情很漂亮我才拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是蘇芳 這樣子行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為尼卡是蘇芳的...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和尼卡只是同一個攝影俱樂部的會員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:06:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會喜歡那粗野的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然老是和我吵嘴 比我高年級還幼稚的要死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒什麼品味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻很意外的對小孩子很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個很不錯的人哦 我可以保證
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 蘇芳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘇芳 塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天輪到你們打掃衛生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界往往在那麼一夜之間就改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛是什麼我現在還不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我知道 塔尼亞已經迎來了那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒有見過真正的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,13年前那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然東京和巴西各出現了一道「門」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東京的那道門被稱為「地獄之門」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴西的那道門被稱為「天國之門」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「門」的附近出現了沒見過的事物和現象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且任何人都無法接近那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太引人注目了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法的啊 這個鏡頭沒有微距的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說的不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小褲褲全露出來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有穿褲襪沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思的是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整個世界變了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也引發了大規模的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這一帶很少受戰爭的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但變化卻無時無刻不在進行著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 蘇芳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 貝拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野貓而已啦 瞄上佩恰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要小心點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博士今天也很忙 在研究所那邊不回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了很豐盛的晚飯 來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 貝拉 聽我說 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天塔尼亞被告白了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被誰 被誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人是尼卡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尼卡不是蘇芳的男朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 完全不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那蘇芳也有喜歡的人嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啦 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨著「門」的出現 真正的星空消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我們所看到的只是虛假的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這片天空中的星星是契約者的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我哦 進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 蘇芳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一種很難理解的感情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然誰都知道這只是因荷爾蒙分泌所引發的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而人卻想將其當作一種寄托
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:10:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很美妙的感覺啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是覺得能夠像你這樣擁有夢想是件很美妙的事 蘇芳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 把我當傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是夢終究會醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像爸爸和媽媽那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啦 媽媽的寫真集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來媽媽過的還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找個時間 我們去看媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去日本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 這...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於現在的我來說 媽媽只是一個毫無意義的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是叫你不要在那房間呆太久嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑是我的弟弟啊 雙胞胎弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是姐弟還是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都和紫苑無關
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法理解這一點的話 你早晚會受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就是一家人 為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還拿著這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在等著啊...所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘇芳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要繼續做夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間只會朝前流逝 永遠無法倒退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘇芳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,契約者沒有心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 佩恰你如何認為呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩恰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:07.72,logo,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(364,464)}第一话 黑猫是不会梦见星星的...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界往往在那麼一夜之間就改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有任何前兆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 塔尼婭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是少見啊 你竟然遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔尼婭 塔尼婭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔尼婭舉止有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔尼婭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔尼婭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早晨你約好一起上學 你也沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 我做了什麼惹你生氣的事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我意識到這是無意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無意義？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本沒有打算為你生小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便做這樣的事也沒有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是為了這個而告白的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 請放手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不放手的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朗塞爾諾福特輻射光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔尼婭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,契 契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔尼婭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉變成契約者沒有任何徵兆 是突然的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性格和行為方式發生天翻地覆的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且一定會引起騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快會被國家機關監禁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且把周圍的人的關於契約者的記憶消除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用爸爸研究的ME
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}ME MemoryEraser（記憶消除）的略稱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔尼婭 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑 怎麼到這兒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這座房子裡不是修了許多秘密通道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓爸爸和我在遇到危險的時候都能立即逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代價已經支付過了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘇芳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快來 到我的房間來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從現在開始 研究所的所有東西都被凍結
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都不許碰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換上衣服 我的衣服不會那麼顯眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是護身符哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.89,0:17:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定記得帶上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不弄丟的話 我們肯定還能再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往研究所的方向去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝拉知道逃出去的路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝拉? 怎麼回事 紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道他們不是在追我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許提問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了 蘇芳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜查的來了 準備逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解 按照預定順序進行回收
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回收的順序是紫苑 博士 資料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一目標消失 似乎已經逃脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,July 知道行蹤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 那個房間裡沒有玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 博士的房間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑 還是FSB
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不是 是個成年人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東洋人 戴著假面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假面?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,April 被竊聽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後封鎖無線 按照C計劃執行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提問的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流星核在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你就沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有嘔吐物和其他的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是隸屬於MI6的April
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑 到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼博士會被殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貝拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘇芳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑呢 紫苑在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了 能請你跟我走一趟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實的話 可以分一點給你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是代價 我也不是那麼想吃這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.99,0:20:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天肌肉又要痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,契約者嗎 真是麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.15,0:21:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是對不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是...
